    <li id="#recipe76">Add a slide-in animation</li>
    <li id="#recipe77">Add sub menus</li>
    <li id="#recipe78">Avoid confusion with menus</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section id="chapter8">
  <h2>8. Toggling Content Visibility</h2>

  <p>There are different ways of hiding content in CSS and HTML. Chapter 8 discusses their pros and cons. You’ll learn how to create disclosure widgets and accordions. The chapter also compares the native &lt;details&gt; element with custom solutions.</p>
  
